{"slug":"golden-faith","title":{"en":"Golden Faith","km":"ពលិកម្មជីវិត"},"description":{"en":"The plot surrounds successful tycoon Ivan Ting Sin Bun, the adopted son of the founder of Ting Fung, a large gold merchant. Ivan discovers that his rival who is seeking a female lawyer's affection turns out to be his long lost brother. But fate plays around with them since the very beginning as Richard Chung Sau Hong not only is Ivan's love rival, but has also already hated Ivan due to a misunderstanding from an illegal money interaction that happened because of a past illegal business involving Ivan's adoptive father, Ting Wing Bong.\n\nTwists and turns in the plot that includes death, legal and business issues, love triangles, cunning scheming and betrayals... all having to do with the close people around Ivan as he finds himself entangled within these problems. All hell breaks loose when Oscar Ting, manipulated by his uncle, Wing Tung, is convinced that Ivan forged their dead father's will and is plotting to take over the family business.","km":"គ្រោងរឿងនិយាយអំពីឧកញ៉ាជោគជ័យ Ivan Ting Sin Bun ដែលជាកូនចិញ្ចឹមរបស់ស្ថាបនិកក្រុមហ៊ុន Ting Fung ដែលជាពាណិជ្ជករមាសធំម្នាក់។ Ivan បានរកឃើញថាគូប្រជែងរបស់គាត់ដែលកំពុងស្វែងរកក្តីស្រលាញ់ពីមេធាវីស្រី បែរជាក្លាយជាបងប្រុសដែលបាត់បង់ជាយូរមកហើយរបស់គាត់។ ប៉ុន្តែវាសនាបានលេងសើចជាមួយពួកគេតាំងពីដើមដំបូងមកម្ល៉េះ ដោយសារ Richard Chung Sau Hong មិនត្រឹមតែជាគូប្រជែងស្នេហារបស់ Ivan ប៉ុណ្ណោះទេ ប៉ុន្តែថែមទាំងស្អប់ Ivan រួចទៅហើយ ដោយសារតែការយល់ច្រឡំពីអន្តរកម្មលុយកាក់ខុសច្បាប់ ដែលបានកើតឡើងដោយសារតែអាជីវកម្មខុសច្បាប់ពីមុន ដែលពាក់ព័ន្ធនឹងឪពុកចិញ្ចឹមរបស់ Ivan គឺ Ting Wing Bong។\n\nរឿងរ៉ាវជាច្រើនរួមមានការស្លាប់ បញ្ហាផ្លូវច្បាប់ និងអាជីវកម្ម ស្នេហាត្រីកោណ ល្បិចកល និងការក្បត់... ទាំងអស់នេះទាក់ទងនឹងមនុស្សជិតស្និទ្ធនៅជុំវិញ Ivan ខណៈដែលគាត់បានរកឃើញថាខ្លួនឯងជាប់ពាក់ព័ន្ធនឹងបញ្ហាទាំងនេះ។ ស្ថានការណ៍ទាំងអស់បានផ្ទុះឡើង នៅពេលដែល Oscar Ting ដែលត្រូវបានពូរបស់គាត់ Wing Tung បានរៀបចំ ជឿជាក់ថា Ivan បានក្លែងបន្លំពាក្យបណ្ដាំរបស់ឪពុកដែលបានស្លាប់របស់ពួកគេ ហើយកំពុងរៀបចំផែនការដើម្បីគ្រប់គ្រងអាជីវកម្មគ្រួសារ។"},"poster":"https://d3tvwjfge35btc.cloudfront.net/Assets/15/714/L_p1004271415.jpg","year":2002,"rating":7.4,"genres":["COMEDY","ACTION","DRAMA","FANTASY","THRILLER","ROMANCE"],"language":"English","episodeCount":45,"episodes":[{"ep":"1","title":{"en":"Episode 1","km":"ភាគទី1"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iamcleanerkak/wivkai/refs/heads/b1/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"2","title":{"en":"Episode 2","km":"ភាគទី2"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iamcleanerkak/wivkai/refs/heads/b2/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"3","title":{"en":"Episode 3","km":"ភាគទី3"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iamcleanerkak/wivkai/refs/heads/b3/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"4","title":{"en":"Episode 4","km":"ភាគទី4"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iamcleanerkak/wivkai/refs/heads/b4/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"5","title":{"en":"Episode 5","km":"ភាគទី5"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iamcleanerkak/wivkai/refs/heads/b5/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"6","title":{"en":"Episode 6","km":"ភាគទី6"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iamcleanerkak/wivkai/refs/heads/b6/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"7","title":{"en":"Episode 7","km":"ភាគទី7"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iamcleanerkak/wivkai/refs/heads/b7/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"8","title":{"en":"Episode 8","km":"ភាគទី8"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iamcleanerkak/wivkai/refs/heads/b8/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"9","title":{"en":"Episode 9","km":"ភាគទី9"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iamcleanerkak/wivkai/refs/heads/b9/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"10","title":{"en":"Episode 10","km":"ភាគទី10"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iamcleanerkak/wivkai/refs/heads/b10/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"11","title":{"en":